Rebecca Broussard https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rebecca_Broussard 0 Rebecca Broussard (born January 3, 1963) is an American actress and model. She was born in Louisville, Kentucky. Broussard has two children with actor Jack Nicholson, whom she was with from 1989 to 1994: daughter Lorraine Nicholson (born April 16, 1990) and son Raymond Nicholson (born February 20, 1992). Since 2001, she has been married to actor Alex Kelly. Rebecca_Broussard ( born January_3_,_1963 ) is an_American_actress_and_model . She was_born in Louisville , Kentucky .
